=============================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                     |NAME|EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |HASH RIGHT OUTER JOIN        |    |2       |7           |
|1 |├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |    |0       |5           |
|2 |│ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t2  |0       |3           |
|3 |│ └─MATERIAL                 |    |0       |3           |
|4 |│   └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |t3  |0       |3           |
|5 |└─TABLE FULL SCAN            |t1  |2       |3           |
=============================================================
